# GnuTLS CVEs in Debian 12 (bookworm) runtime images.
#
# All DCC services use debian:12-slim as the runtime base and install libpq5,
# which pulls in libgnutls30 as a transitive dependency. None of our services
# use GnuTLS or DTLS directly — they connect to local PostgreSQL over TCP and
# to the DCC node over gRPC (backed by hyper/tonic, not GnuTLS).
#
# These CVEs are pending Debian 12 security backport. Track at:
# https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/source-package/gnutls28
#
# Justification filed: 2026-06-09. Review when Debian releases the backport.

CVE-2026-42009
CVE-2026-3833
CVE-2026-33846
CVE-2026-42010
CVE-2026-33845
